  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Cast your line, slow down, and enjoy the simple pleasure of fishing</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a <strong>cozy, stylized fishing game</strong> designed to be played at your own pace. Explore calm waters, catch charming and unusual fish, and enjoy a relaxing experience focused on <strong>satisfaction, atmosphere, and fun</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every catch feels rewarding. Every moment is unhurried. <br> <br>🐟 <strong><i>A World Full of Charm</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From funny little fish to mysterious stitched creatures, every asset is crafted with a playful, cozy style. This is a world where fishing isn’t about competition — it’s about <strong>comfort, curiosity, and quiet satisfaction</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>🌊 <strong><i>Relax, Fish, Repeat</i></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎣 <strong>Satisfying fishing mechanics</strong> that feel good from cast to catch</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐠 <strong>Cute, stylized fish</strong> with unique designs and personalities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌅 <strong>Cozy, low-poly visuals</strong> with warm colors and soft lighting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎧 A calm atmosphere made for unwinding</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧘 <strong>Single-player experience</strong> — no pressure, no rush, just you and the water</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎣 Grab your rod. Take a breath. Let the water do the rest.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Cast your line, slow down, and enjoy the simple pleasure of fishing</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a <strong>cozy, stylized fishing game</strong> designed to be played at your own pace. Explore calm waters, catch charming and unusual fish, and enjoy a relaxing experience focused on <strong>satisfaction, atmosphere, and fun</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every catch feels rewarding. Every moment is unhurried. <br> <br>🐟 <strong><i>A World Full of Charm</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From funny little fish to mysterious stitched creatures, every asset is crafted with a playful, cozy style. This is a world where fishing isn’t about competition — it’s about <strong>comfort, curiosity, and quiet satisfaction</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>🌊 <strong><i>Relax, Fish, Repeat</i></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎣 <strong>Satisfying fishing mechanics</strong> that feel good from cast to catch</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐠 <strong>Cute, stylized fish</strong> with unique designs and personalities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌅 <strong>Cozy, low-poly visuals</strong> with warm colors and soft lighting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎧 A calm atmosphere made for unwinding</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧘 <strong>Single-player experience</strong> — no pressure, no rush, just you and the water</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎣 Grab your rod. Take a breath. Let the water do the rest.</p>",
